7 ORGANIZATIONS TO CONDUCT LIVE GAMBLING UNDER CERTAIN CIRCUMSTANCES; GRANTING
8 EXEMPTIONS FOR FEES; REVISING LAWS RELATING TO ANTIQUE GAMBLING DEVICES; EXTENDING
9 RULEMAKING AUTHORITY; PROVIDING A DEFINITION; AMENDING SECTIONS 23-5-112, 23-5-153, 23-5-
10 161, 23-5-162, 23-5-311, 23-5-313, 23-5-406, 23-5-407, 23-5-408, 23-5-409, 23-5-410, 23-5-414, 23-5-424, 23-
