13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF MONTANA:
14
15 NEW SECTION. Section 1. Wild west casino nights -- purpose -- definition. (1) [Sections 1
16 through 5] may be referred to as the "Wild West Casino Nights Act".
17 (2) The purpose of [sections 1 through 5] is to allow for historical education and fundraising for
18 living history nonprofit organizations.
19 (3) Unless the context requires otherwise, for the purposes of this part, the term "wild west casino
20 night" means a fundraising event during which wagers may be made in antique gambling activities authorized
21 under 23-5-311 through the use of imitation money that may be purchased by participants.
22
23 NEW SECTION. Section 2. Wild west casino nights authorized. (1) A living history nonprofit
24 organization may conduct or participate in a wild west casino night. Entities covered under this section may
25 consist of the following:
26 (a) a nonprofit living history organization;
27 (b) an individual living history volunteer; or
28 (c) a history reenacting organization.
